{"result": {"folders": ["lecture3"], "nr": 992, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "created": "2017-02-28T01:49:36Z", "bucket_order": 3, "no_answer_followup": 0, "change_log": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "ie7xy5sipx51qz", "data": "izovl421hm36wd", "type": "create", "when": "2017-02-28T01:49:36Z"}], "bucket_name": "Today", "history": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "ie7xy5sipx51qz", "subject": "函数调用和系统调用的“选择”问题", "created": "2017-02-28T01:49:36Z", "content": "<p>向勇老师在MOOC第3.4节8:06左右时提到&#xff1a;</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>“最后我们还有一个问题需要来讨论&#xff0c;就是我在什么时候用系统调用&#xff0c;什么时候用函数调用。”</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>一开始我对这句话不是很理解。一些功能&#xff08;如文件读写&#xff09;由内核态完成&#xff0c;我们只能用系统调用实现&#xff0c;只用函数调用不能实现。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>但实际上这个问题针对的是操作系统设计者&#xff0c;而不是操作系统使用者。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>在软件工程的实践中&#xff0c;某些功能是放在用户态还是内核态实现是由OS开发者选择的。放在内核态能有更高的效率&#xff0c;但如果功能实现有漏洞&#xff0c;在内核态会造成更大的安全隐患&#xff0c;适合放在内核态。在某些Linux版本中&#xff0c;GUI被放在内核态实现&#xff0c;有些则在用户态实现。对于我们这种OS设计者&#xff0c;我们应该对功能分配做出最好的判断。</p>"}], "type": "note", "tags": ["lecture3", "student"], "tag_good": [{"role": "instructor", "name": "Yu Chen", "endorser": {}, "admin": true, "photo": "1378950179_35.png", "id": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "photo_url": "https://d1b10bmlvqabco.cloudfront.net/photos/hcrrjuyequh4bt/1378950179_35.png", "us": false, "class_sections": ["课程设计_i5j09fnsl7k5x0", "清华学生_i5j09fnsl7k5x0", "所有老师和助教_i5j09fnsl7k5x0", "os2018spring_i5j09fnsl7k5x0"], "facebook_id": null}], "unique_views": 123, "children": [], "tag_good_arr": ["hcrrjuyequh4bt"], "id": "izovl40ssrw6wb", "config": {}, "status": "active", "drafts": null, "request_instructor": 0, "request_instructor_me": false, "bookmarked": 4, "num_favorites": 0, "my_favorite": false, "is_bookmarked": false, "is_tag_good": false, "q_edits": [], "i_edits": [], "s_edits": [], "t": 1643168947553, "default_anonymity": "no"}, "error": null, "aid": "kyv0d6cheh64wb"}